    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <header class="hero">
        <div class="overlay"></div>
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Petroleum Engineering</h1>
            <p>Explore the science and technology behind extracting and refining the world's energy resources</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- About Section -->
    <section class="section" id="about">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">What is Petroleum Engineering?</h2>
            <div class="content-wrapper">
                <div class="text-content">
                    <p>Petroleum engineering focuses on the exploration, extraction, and production of oil and natural gas. It combines principles of geology, physics, and engineering to design processes that efficiently recover hydrocarbons from subsurface reservoirs while prioritizing safety and environmental sustainability.</p>
                    <p>As a petroleum engineer, you'll work on drilling operations, reservoir management, and production optimization. You'll use advanced technologies to locate reserves, design drilling systems, and enhance recovery methods, contributing to the global energy supply. This field requires a deep understanding of subsurface dynamics and innovative approaches to address declining resources and environmental concerns.</p>
                    <p>With the energy sector transitioning toward sustainability, petroleum engineers are also exploring roles in carbon capture, geothermal energy, and alternative fuels, making this a dynamic and evolving career path.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Key Areas Section -->
    <section class="section bg-dark" id="key-areas">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Key Areas of Study</h2>
            <p class="section-intro">Petroleum Engineering encompasses critical disciplines for efficient and sustainable hydrocarbon extraction:</p>
            
            <div class="cards-grid three-columns">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-hard-hat"></i> Drilling Engineering</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Design and execution of drilling operations to access hydrocarbon reservoirs safely and efficiently.</p>
                        <ul class="skills-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Well Design</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Casing, drilling fluids</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Drilling Techniques</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Directional, horizontal drilling</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Blowout Prevention</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Safety systems, BOPs</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-layer-group"></i> Reservoir Engineering</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Analysis and management of subsurface reservoirs to maximize hydrocarbon recovery.</p>
                        <ul class="skills-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Reservoir Simulation</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Modeling fluid flow</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Enhanced Recovery</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Waterflooding, CO2 injection</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Reserve Estimation</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Volumetric, decline curve analysis</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-industry"></i> Production Engineering</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Optimization of hydrocarbon production from wells to surface facilities.</p>
                        <ul class="skills-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Well Completion</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Perforation, stimulation</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Artificial Lift</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Pumps, gas lift systems</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Production Optimization</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Flow assurance, choke management</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="cards-grid three-columns" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-globe"></i> Formation Evaluation</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Techniques to assess reservoir properties using geological and geophysical data.</p>
                        <ul class="skills-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Well Logging</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Wireline, LWD tools</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Core Analysis</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Porosity, permeability</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Seismic Interpretation</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Reservoir mapping</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-leaf"></i> Environmental Management</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Strategies to minimize environmental impact and ensure regulatory compliance in petroleum operations.</p>
                        <ul class="skills-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Carbon Capture</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">CCS technologies</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Waste Management</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Drilling waste, produced water</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Regulatory Compliance</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">EIA, environmental standards</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-cogs"></i> Petroleum Economics</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Evaluation of project feasibility and risk in oil and gas developments.</p>
                        <ul class="skills-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Cost Estimation</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">CAPEX, OPEX analysis</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Risk Analysis</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Monte Carlo, decision trees</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Project Valuation</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">NPV, IRR calculations</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

