                        <ul>
                            <li>• Carbon Capture and Storage (CCS)</li>
                            <li>• Geothermal Energy</li>
                            <li>• Enhanced Oil Recovery (EOR)</li>
                            <li>• Offshore and Deepwater Exploration</li>
